================
description
================

1) This program accept file name from user which contains information of emloyee,
	and read all contents of that file.
2) Required filename will be taken from command line

================
about the code
================

	input	:	file_name
	output	:	employee information
 			
=============
How to run
=============

	make	:	compile the code and generates executable file as "myexe"
	make run:	run the executable with command line argument
			for this you have to pass parameter as: 
			
			$ make run p="parameter_value"
	
=============
NOTE
=============

	1)If the given file is unable to open, it will display the appropriate reason.
	2) this program implements "$cat" command.
